Package: Relsize
Type: Package
Title: Calculate the sample size using the Relative Time method under NPH and NPT secnerios
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2021-11-01
Author: Palash Sharma
Maintainer: Palash Sharma <psharma4@kumc.edu> 
Description: This package helps to calulate the sample size using the time to event data under relative time framework. Also, can be used for stochastic curtailment method for futility monitoring purposes. 
    Sample size restimation can also be done using this package.
